<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>fsociety - Secure System</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Rajdhani:wght@300;400;600;700&family=Share+Tech+Mono&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        body {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0a0e27 0%, #050811 100%);
            color: #00ff41;
            font-family: 'Rajdhani', sans-serif;
            overflow-x: hidden;
            min-height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            padding: 20px;
        }

        body::before {
            content: '';
            position: fixed;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            background-image: 
                linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(0, 255, 65, 0.03) 1px, transparent 1px),
                linear-gradient(rgba(0, 255, 65, 0.03) 1px, transparent 1px);
            background-size: 50px 50px;
            pointer-events: none;
            z-index: 0;
        }

        .container {
            position: relative;
            z-index: 1;
            max-width: 900px;
            width: 100%;
        }

        .terminal {
            background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.95);
            border: 3px solid #ff006e;
            border-radius: 4px;
            padding: 40px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 40px rgba(255, 0, 110, 0.3), inset 0 0 20px rgba(0, 255, 65, 0.05);
        }

        .header {
            border-bottom: 2px solid #ff006e;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            padding-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .title {
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            text-shadow: 0 0 10px #ff006e;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        .subtitle {
            color: #00ff41;
            font-size: 1rem;
            letter-spacing: 2px;
            font-family: 'Share Tech Mono', monospace;
        }

        .line {
            margin: 15px 0;
            font-family: 'Share Tech Mono', monospace;
            font-size: 1rem;
        }

        .prompt {
            color: #00ff41;
        }

        .status {
            color: #ff006e;
            font-weight: bold;
        }

        .info {
            margin: 30px 0;
            border-left: 3px solid #ff006e;
            padding-left: 20px;
            color: #e6e6e6;
        }

        .challenge-box {
            background: rgba(255, 0, 110, 0.1);
            border: 2px solid #ff006e;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            border-radius: 4px;
        }

        .command {
            background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);
            border: 1px solid #00ff41;
            padding: 10px 15px;
            margin: 10px 0;
            border-radius: 2px;
            font-family: 'Share Tech Mono', monospace;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            overflow-x: auto;
        }

        .button-group {
            margin-top: 30px;
            display: flex;
            gap: 15px;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
        }

        button {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ff006e, #d800ff);
            border: none;
            color: white;
            padding: 12px 30px;
            border-radius: 2px;
            cursor: pointer;
            font-family: 'Rajdhani', sans-serif;
            font-weight: 600;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            transition: all 0.3s;
            box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(255, 0, 110, 0.3);
        }

        button:hover {
            box-shadow: 0 0 40px rgba(255, 0, 110, 0.6);
            transform: translateY(-2px);
        }

        .warning {
            color: #ffb700;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            font-weight: bold;
        }

        code {
            background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);
            color: #00ff41;
            padding: 2px 6px;
            border-radius: 2px;
            font-family: 'Share Tech Mono', monospace;
        }

        .section {
            margin: 30px 0;
        }

        h2 {
            color: #ff006e;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            letter-spacing: 2px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="terminal">
            <div class="header">
                <div class="title">fsociety</div>
                <div class="subtitle">$ SECURE SYSTEM ACCESS INTERFACE</div>
            </div>

            <div class="line"><span class="prompt">$</span> system_status.sh</div>
            <div class="line"><span class="status">[WARNING] SYSTEM VULNERABILITY DETECTED</span></div>
            <div class="line"></div>

            <div class="info">
                <h2>Challenge Information</h2>
                <p>A critical vulnerability exists in the system configuration parser.</p>
                <p>The application processes YAML data without proper validation.</p>
                <p>Your objective: Exploit the vulnerability to retrieve the hidden flag.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="section">
                <h2>Available Endpoints</h2>
                <div class="command">GET /api/system-config?data=&lt;YAML_PAYLOAD&gt;</div>
                <p style="margin-top: 10px; color: #999;">Process YAML configuration data</p>
                <div class="command" style="margin-top: 15px;">GET /admin/dashboard</div>
                <p style="margin-top: 10px; color: #999;">Admin panel (may reveal secrets)</p>
            </div>

            <div class="challenge-box">
                <h2>Challenge</h2>
                <p style="margin: 15px 0;">Find and exploit the YAML deserialization vulnerability to retrieve the flag.</p>
                <p style="color: #00ff41; margin: 15px 0;"><strong>Flag Format:</strong> <code>fsociety{...}</code></p>
                <p style="color: #ffb700; margin: 15px 0; font-weight: bold;">⚠️ This is a real vulnerability. Use responsibly.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="section">
                <h2>Tools</h2>
                <p style="margin: 10px 0;">Try one of these approaches:</p>
                <div class="command">curl "http://localhost:3000/api/system-config?data=test"</div>
                <div class="command" style="margin-top: 10px;">curl "http://localhost:3000/admin/dashboard"</div>
            </div>

            <div class="button-group">
                <button onclick="checkEndpoint('/api/system-config?data=test')">Test Endpoint</button>
                <button onclick="checkEndpoint('/admin/dashboard')">Check Admin</button>
                <button onclick="alert('Hints available on main CTF website')">Get Hints</button>
            </div>

            <div class="line" style="margin-top: 40px; color: #999;">
                <span class="prompt">$</span> STATUS: AWAITING EXPLOITATION...
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <script>
        function checkEndpoint(endpoint) {
            fetch(endpoint)
                .then(r => r.json())
                .then(d => {
                    console.log('Response:', d);
                    alert('Check browser console (F12) for response');
                })
                .catch(e => alert('Error: ' + e.message));
        }
    </script>
</body>
</html>
